name: Spiel Mit Mir
wikiSummary: "Spiel mit mir" is a song by the German Industrial-Metal band Rammstein on their album Sehnsucht. The song is about incest between two siblings.
wikiText:
"Spiel mit mir" is a song by the German Industrial-Metal band Rammstein on their album Sehnsucht. The song is about incest between two siblings.
